{"tid":1010894,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【車公靈籤】香港求得86籤中籤 解籤師傅：認真不好實為下籤","createTime":"2019-02-06T10:44:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T15:48:40.000Z","uid":49391,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e0a3517ce82cf8501dc90b86db26dc6249d49d77","tid":1010894,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T10:44:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jOGxf4e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjOGxf4e.jpg&h=a69c030b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n劉業強為香港求得第86籤。<br />\n新界鄉議局主席劉業強按傳統，於年初二早上率沙田鄉事委員會代表及鄉紳，到車公廟為香港求籤祈福。劉業強為香港求得第86籤中籤，籤文為「石田為業喜非常，畫餅將來未見香；怎曉田耕耘不得，那知餅食不充腸。」籤文解為「出入謹慎，家宅不吉，自身平安，求財不遂。」<br />\n<br />\n劉業強指籤文解「香港基礎非常好，政府施政需市民支持」，才有更好的未來。大會官方解籤師表示，首句是相當不錯，指香港的先天條件不錯，要如何使市民安居樂業，要由政府施行下去，但他未有解釋其餘3句籤文。<br />\n<br />\n車公廟場外解籤師傅陳天恩表示，此籤「認真不好，非常之差，實為下籤」，因籤頭為話梅止渴，即「得個睇字」，而田地布滿石頭不能耕種，畫出的餅亦不能吃。他認為與填海、收緊長者綜援、沙中線及派4000元有關，即好看但不中用，對香港沒有利益。對於官方解籤師並未解釋餘下籤文，他認為對方「不敢再解下去」。他建議市民唯有自保，「不要買無謂嘢，有用先買，要珍惜錢財。」<br />\n<br />\n場外另一位解籤師傅李奎賢指：「一定要4句籤文融合來解讀，只解一句並不恰當。」他認為政府現時處於內訌，內部有爭執，特首的民望又不斷下跌，認為應先提高民望。他又認為籤文指經濟不好，內藏煞機，因中美貿易戰始終影響香港。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1427232/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1427232%2F&d=fwxP8pl6u%2F9ArYBpkrNVTGCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=27d3a2bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1427232%2F&h=72d416e8\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1427232/</a>"},{"pid":"1823bbd6034ed88c919818b416bc26694470772f","tid":1010894,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T10:46:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbe6957c1151573b849da859ac22d5f344bd76bc","tid":1010894,"uid":49391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T10:48:36.000Z","msg":"覺得幾準,蕭生都話持有多D現金/外匯穩陣D,佢話佢自已經將三橦物業轉返做現金<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/qUxvafc_ZO8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FqUxvafc_ZO8&d=fwxP8pl6u%2F9ArYBpkrNVTGCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=0d39fa07\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/qUxvafc_ZO8</a>"},{"pid":"7687516d82e154e8618a7fdccf2b9c6cd1435bcf","tid":1010894,"uid":69484,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T10:55:28.000Z","msg":"車公真係靈驗 <br />\n年年都中 03年就下下籤"},{"pid":"5bd82a92e9701ea15ac816d2c2c089f0a9210755","tid":1010894,"uid":138233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T10:59:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"517c56e9f991a11a4cc665f9c8bf9ab90632380f","tid":1010894,"uid":147292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T11:02:39.000Z","msg":"mola mola"},{"pid":"2d2a949b7d2321bea88563b02ce3a733050f545d","tid":1010894,"uid":25858,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"7687516d82e154e8618a7fdccf2b9c6cd1435bcf","tid":1010894,"uid":69484,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T10:55:28.000Z","msg":"車公真係靈驗 <br />\n年年都中 03年就下下籤"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T11:03:12.000Z","msg":"志平個年專登解錯簽文！而家睇下佢下埸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b4d9691e291edd8ca9fdadc30a119f4e1b964fa","tid":1010894,"uid":200818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T11:06:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b8c9cd4f0756b1ed3a4477b064538ede47ba15c","tid":1010894,"uid":50310,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"2d2a949b7d2321bea88563b02ce3a733050f545d","tid":1010894,"uid":25858,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"7687516d82e154e8618a7fdccf2b9c6cd1435bcf","tid":1010894,"uid":69484,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T10:55:28.000Z","msg":"車公真係靈驗 <br />\n年年都中 03年就下下籤"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T11:03:12.000Z","msg":"志平個年專登解錯簽文！而家睇下佢下埸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T11:08:13.000Z","msg":"呢樣真呀！<br />\n當眾侮辱神明<br />\n仲衰撚過唔求<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"737224313862dc59e6d077cf1f68d1b16103f48a","tid":1010894,"uid":2521,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T11:08:20.000Z","msg":"後面3句兜唔到，索性唔講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37df5afeedb4349ffdd6745f9bd088e252435537","tid":1010894,"uid":124140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T11:09:06.000Z","msg":"籤文睇落都似係講計劃既野當實行既時候先知比理想差<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64bc52f31256354e9a896ab81709675769385e4e","tid":1010894,"uid":49391,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T11:48:43.000Z","msg":"家宅不吉，自身平安<br />\n呢句野看似矛盾,我覺得其實意有所指:家即係祖國指中國,不吉當然係指黑天鵝同灰犀牛呢兩大類問題,當中又牽涉政治同經濟兩個層面<br />\n<br />\n自身係指香港本身,劉業強無講錯,香港基礎非常好,包括法制同經濟兩方面,同埋仲有少少獨立性,甚麼黑天鵝、灰犀牛殺到埋身都唔會對香港有太大衝擊,所以係平安<br />\n<br />\n利申:唔識解籤,9UP下"},{"pid":"d40c41115db481e24b1f8b0c883fa8a7b9c0df28","tid":1010894,"uid":511,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T12:20:12.000Z","msg":"其實條撚屌憑咩代表全香港求籤，都on lun 99<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e22acf07462bf339269c6fd8bb524d6ed2d438d3","tid":1010894,"uid":11156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T15:48:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}